data.description: Prime Corner Lot Gem! This home is better than new, with a covered rear patio adorned by charming string lights for ambiance. Luxurious vinyl plank flooring and exquisite gray-painted cabinets grace the downstairs. The kitchen shines with hardware-accented cabinets, a gas range, and stainless steel appliances. A corner walk-in pantry and spacious island flow into the dining and family room. Glass sliding doors open to a covered back porch. Extras include an oversized powder room and a mud/storage area and Polyaspartic flooring in garage. Upstairs, the primary bedroom boasts a walk-in closet and an adjoining storage closet. The primary bath is well-appointed with double sinks, a garden tub, and a separate shower. Secondary bedrooms share a bathroom and linen closet. Enjoy community amenities like walking trails, parks, a splash pad, and more. Easy access to 290, Grand Parkway, outlets, medical facilities, shopping, and dining. Don't miss this opportunity!
